But some investors might prefer a simpler strategy@#%^&*29
then hedging their individual holdings.@#%^&*29
They can do this@#%^&*30
by purchasing "index puts,"@#%^&*30
which are simply put options on indexes@#%^&*30
that match broad baskets of stocks.@#%^&*30
For instance, the most popular index option is the S&P 100 option,@#%^&*31
commonly called the OEX.@#%^&*31
