Unlike options on individual issues, index options are settled only in cash,@#%^&*33
and no stock is ever tendered.@#%^&*33
But while index options are convenient,@#%^&*34
they have several disadvantages.@#%^&*34
For one thing, an investor's portfolio might not closely match the S&P 100.@#%^&*35
As a result, the OEX insurance may or may not fully protect an investor's holdings in the event of a market decline.@#%^&*36
